Dealing With Errors
Check you understand the difference between the following two blocks of code by running them.

try:
    print(listings['Trendy Terrace'])
except KeyError as e:
    print("Error found")
    print(e)


try:
    print(listings.get('Trendy Terrace','Not Found'))
